Process Hellmann's(R) or Best Foods(R) Real Mayonnaise, salsa and lime juice in blender until smooth, adding water if necessary to thin to dressing consistency. Season, if desired, with salt and pepper. Arrange lettuce in large bowl and toss with 1/2 of the dressing. Gently toss in remaining ingredients except corn chips. Drizzle with remaining dressing, then top with corn chips.